    feat(core): per-layer profiler (--profile), adapted from TensorRT samples

    Add yolov8::Profiler (nvinfer1::IProfiler) modeled on the TensorRT sample
    SimpleProfiler; the new --profile flag attaches it to the execution context and
    prints a per-layer time/percent/calls table on exit (a C++ counterpart to
    trt-profile.py). IProfiler is identical on TensorRT 8 and 10, so no version
    branch is needed. ACKNOWLEDGMENTS.md credits TensorRT samples (Apache-2.0) and
    gulrak/filesystem (MIT).

    🤖 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)

